# 

 
 # 题目背景 
<p>NOIP2015提高组&nbsp;D2T2</p> 

 
 # 题目描述 
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;">有两个仅包含小写英文字母的字符串&nbsp;A&nbsp;和&nbsp;B。现在要从字符串&nbsp;A&nbsp;中取出&nbsp;k&nbsp;个互不重</span><br class="contentbr" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;" />
<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;">叠的非空子串,然后把这&nbsp;k&nbsp;个子串按照其在字符串&nbsp;A&nbsp;中出现的顺序依次连接起来得到一&nbsp;个新的字符串,请问有多少种方案可以使得这个新串与字符串&nbsp;B&nbsp;相等?注意:子串取出&nbsp;的位置不同也认为是不同的方案。</span></p> 

 
 # 输入格式 
<p><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;">输入文件名为&nbsp;substring.in。</span><br class="contentbr" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;" />
<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;">第一行是三个正整数&nbsp;n,m,k,分别表示字符串&nbsp;A&nbsp;的长度,字符串&nbsp;B&nbsp;的长度,以及问</span><br class="contentbr" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;" />
<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;">题描述中所提到的&nbsp;k,每两个整数之间用一个空格隔开。&nbsp;第二行包含一个长度为&nbsp;n&nbsp;的字符串,表示字符串&nbsp;A。&nbsp;第三行包含一个长度为&nbsp;m&nbsp;的字符串,表示字符串&nbsp;B。</span></p> 

 
 # 输出格式 
<p><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;">输出文件名为&nbsp;substring.out。&nbsp;输出共一行,包含一个整数,表示所求方案数。由于答案可能很大,所以这里要求</span><b style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">输出答案对&nbsp;1,000,000,007&nbsp;取模的结果。</b></p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">样例一：<samp style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 1em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><u style="box-sizing: border-box;">aab</u></strong>&nbsp;aab&nbsp;/&nbsp;aab&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><u style="box-sizing: border-box;">aab</u></strong></samp></p>

<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, 'Microsoft YaHei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;">对于第&nbsp;1&nbsp;组数据:1&le;n&le;500,1&le;m&le;50,k=1;</span><br class="contentbr" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: inline; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;" />
